post_collections

public JSONObject post_collections(java.lang.String title,
                                   java.lang.String path,
                                   boolean isProfileSet,
                                   java.lang.String[] photo_ids,
                                   int position)
500px POST_collections. Creates new a collection.

Parameters:
title - (required) Ñ Title for the collection.
path - (required) Ñ Path where the collection will be accessible at 500px.com/user/sets/:path.
isProfileSet - Kind of the Collection to be created Recognized values: false - Portfolio Set, true - Profile Set.
photo_ids - String array of photo_ids to add into this collection.
position - Position of the collection in the list of collections.
Returns:
JSON response. See 500px API for details.

Remark: Requires OAuth authentication.
